stateDiagram-v2
    [*] --> Pending: Task Created
    
    Pending --> InProgress: Start Task
    Pending --> Deleted: Delete Task
    
    InProgress --> Paused: Pause Task
    InProgress --> Completed: Complete Task
    InProgress --> Deleted: Delete Task
    
    Paused --> InProgress: Resume Task
    Paused --> Completed: Complete Task
    Paused --> Deleted: Delete Task
    
    Completed --> [*]: Task Finished
    Deleted --> [*]: Task Removed
    
    note right of Pending
        No timing data
        Estimated pomodoros set
    end note
    
    note right of InProgress
        started_at timestamp set
        Active PomodoroSession created
        Timer running
    end note
    
    note right of Paused
        Active session paused
        Can resume multiple times
        Time accumulates
    end note
    
    note right of Completed
        ended_at timestamp set
        Total focus time calculated
        All sessions completed
    end note